864
00:35:22,020 --> 00:35:22,900
to be the madam?

865
00:35:22,900 --> 00:35:23,820
Mother...

866
00:35:24,340 --> 00:35:25,300
Since she's confessed,

867
00:35:25,420 --> 00:35:26,380
Yunyi,

868
00:35:26,820 --> 00:35:27,780
take her away.

869
00:35:28,140 --> 00:35:29,020
I believe

870
00:35:29,020 --> 00:35:30,860
the Judicial Review
will handle it fairly.

871
00:35:31,220 --> 00:35:32,140
- Mother.
- Yes.

872
00:35:32,140 --> 00:35:33,500
How can you confess to this?

873
00:35:33,580 --> 00:35:34,450
Qilan,

874
00:35:34,460 --> 00:35:35,460
this is all my fault.

875
00:35:35,460 --> 00:35:36,300
Mother,

876
00:35:36,300 --> 00:35:37,540
please don't let this

877
00:35:37,540 --> 00:35:38,780
ruin your future.

878
00:35:39,420 --> 00:35:41,140
Father,

879
00:35:41,140 --> 00:35:42,620
please save Mother.

880
00:35:42,710 --> 00:35:43,920
She's been with you for decades

881
00:35:43,920 --> 00:35:45,420
as your partner, Father.

882
00:35:45,420 --> 00:35:47,220
Father, I beg you.

883
00:35:47,660 --> 00:35:50,060
She has done such shameless things.

884
00:35:50,380 --> 00:35:53,260
It's ruined the reputation
of our family.

885
00:35:53,260 --> 00:35:54,180
Father.

886
00:35:55,460 --> 00:35:56,420
She...

887
00:35:58,220 --> 00:35:59,180
She...

888
00:36:02,140 --> 00:36:03,100
Father.

889
00:36:08,540 --> 00:36:09,500
I...

890
00:36:09,900 --> 00:36:11,780
I feel so bad.

891
00:36:16,940 --> 00:36:19,060
(Shen Mansion)

892
00:36:22,460 --> 00:36:23,420
Jiangli.

893
00:36:24,380 --> 00:36:25,340
Jiangli.

894
00:36:25,540 --> 00:36:26,780
Jiangli, please listen to me.

895
00:36:26,780 --> 00:36:28,460
I didn't know anything
about Lian Wantang.

896
00:36:28,620 --> 00:36:30,340
Please spare my mother. I'm begging you.

897
00:36:30,340 --> 00:36:31,900
- My mother...
- She's confessed.

898
00:36:32,660 --> 00:36:33,740
As for the rest,

899
00:36:34,700 --> 00:36:36,100
it has nothing to do with my wife.

900
00:36:36,620 --> 00:36:37,580
Let's go home.

901
00:36:37,740 --> 00:36:39,260
Master Jingming, Consort Jiangli.

902
00:36:51,820 --> 00:36:52,660
Hey.

903
00:36:52,660 --> 00:36:53,740
I want hot water.

904
00:36:53,740 --> 00:36:54,900
Go get me some.

905
00:36:56,740 --> 00:36:58,580
Did you hear me? Are you deaf?

906
00:36:59,260 --> 00:37:00,580
Do you know who I am?

907
00:37:04,500 --> 00:37:05,560
Don't let anyone find out.

908
00:37:05,900 --> 00:37:06,860
Go inside.

909
00:37:08,180 --> 00:37:09,140
- Qilan.
- Mother.

910
00:37:09,820 --> 00:37:11,340
Get me out of here.

911
00:37:11,340 --> 00:37:12,860
This place is so cold and damp.

912
00:37:12,860 --> 00:37:14,220
I'm so scared.

913
00:37:14,220 --> 00:37:16,220
- Mother.
- I can't stay here.

914
00:37:16,220 --> 00:37:17,300
Mother, don't worry.

915
00:37:17,300 --> 00:37:18,660
I'll get you out of here.

916
00:37:18,660 --> 00:37:19,620
Qilan.

917
00:37:19,780 --> 00:37:21,660
Am I going to be exiled?

918
00:37:22,100 --> 00:37:24,060
I've heard that those who are exiled

919
00:37:24,060 --> 00:37:25,580
never return alive.

920
00:37:25,780 --> 00:37:27,780
Most of them die on the road.

921
00:37:27,900 --> 00:37:29,460
You have to get me out of here

922
00:37:29,460 --> 00:37:30,460
before the verdict.

923
00:37:30,460 --> 00:37:31,660
Please, Qilan.

924
00:37:31,660 --> 00:37:33,340
Mother, don't worry.

925
00:37:33,620 --> 00:37:34,540
I'll beg Jiangli.

926
00:37:34,540 --> 00:37:36,020
She can hit or scold me if she wants.

927
00:37:36,020 --> 00:37:37,620
I'll do whatever she asks me to.

928
00:37:37,800 --> 00:37:39,180
I won't let anything happen to you.

929
00:37:39,180 --> 00:37:40,540
Qilan, listen to me.

930
00:37:40,780 --> 00:37:43,020
Shen Jiangli will not let me go.

931
00:37:43,300 --> 00:37:44,560
You should go to Master Jingxiu.

932
00:37:44,660 --> 00:37:45,900
After all, I'm your mother,

933
00:37:46,100 --> 00:37:47,460
and you're his only woman.

934
00:37:47,460 --> 00:37:48,740
He won't ignore this.

935
00:37:48,740 --> 00:37:49,660
Mother,

936
00:37:49,900 --> 00:37:51,500
this can't involve Master Jingxiu.

937
00:37:51,900 --> 00:37:52,980
But don't worry.

938
00:37:53,260 --> 00:37:55,100
I will risk everything to save you.

939
00:37:55,260 --> 00:37:56,660
Mother, wait for me.

940
00:38:07,820 --> 00:38:08,780
Thank you.

941
00:38:09,740 --> 00:38:10,700
Why?

942
00:38:11,620 --> 00:38:12,580
Thank you for everything

943
00:38:13,580 --> 00:38:15,340
you've done for my mother.

944
00:38:16,860 --> 00:38:17,780
And thank you

945
00:38:17,780 --> 00:38:19,460
for always standing by me.

946
00:38:26,260 --> 00:38:27,580
I just want you to be happy.

947
00:38:29,500 --> 00:38:30,460
Besides,

948
00:38:31,220 --> 00:38:32,940
Mrs. Shen is my mother-in-law.

949
00:38:33,740 --> 00:38:34,700
Of course,

950
00:38:34,820 --> 00:38:35,900
I can't just stand by.

951
00:38:38,700 --> 00:38:40,340
Zou deserves her punishment,

952
00:38:41,860 --> 00:38:43,220
