954
00:38:48,700 --> 00:38:50,100
that almost blinded me

955
00:38:51,020 --> 00:38:52,660
and let the culprit go free.

956
00:38:53,500 --> 00:38:54,460
It seems

957
00:38:54,820 --> 00:38:55,980
your sister

958
00:38:57,060 --> 00:38:58,900
is not as innocent as you thought.

959
00:39:00,820 --> 00:39:01,780
Yes.

960
00:39:02,540 --> 00:39:03,540
I didn't expect

961
00:39:04,980 --> 00:39:06,220
the inner chambers

962
00:39:07,100 --> 00:39:08,500
to be so dark

963
00:39:09,260 --> 00:39:11,300
that they could change
someone so easily.

964
00:39:11,900 --> 00:39:13,180
Zou was like that,

965
00:39:13,580 --> 00:39:14,660
and now it seems

966
00:39:15,580 --> 00:39:17,420
Shen Qilan is the same.

967
00:39:17,980 --> 00:39:20,340
For status and power,

968
00:39:20,860 --> 00:39:22,580
they slowly lose themselves,

969
00:39:23,500 --> 00:39:25,660
trampling on others,

970
00:39:26,300 --> 00:39:27,620
even others' lives.

971
00:39:32,340 --> 00:39:33,420
I hope my mother

972
00:39:34,740 --> 00:39:37,340
won't be trapped there again
in her next life.

